  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      libid3tag is an ID3 tag manipulation library with full support for reading
      ID3v1, ID3v1.1, ID3v2.2, ID3v2.3, and ID3v2.4 tags, as well as support for
      writing ID3v1, ID3v1.1, and ID3v2.4 tags.
    </para>

